    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Rich Blessings Assured Country Dwellers</strong>&mdash;The earth has blessings hidden in her depths for those who have courage and will and perseverance to gather her treasures.... Many farmers have failed to secure adequate returns from their land because they have undertaken the work as though it was a degrading employment; they do not see that there is a blessing in it for themselves and their families.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">6<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"FE 326.1\" data-link=\"32.1315\">Fundamentals of Christian Education, 326, 327</span>.</span></a></sup>",
