    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Find Spiritual Lessons in Daily Living</strong>&mdash;God has surrounded us with nature&apos;s beautiful scenery to attract and interest the mind. It is His design that we should associate the glories of nature with His character. If we faithfully study the book of nature, we shall find it a fruitful source for contemplating the infinite love and power of God.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">10<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"MYP 365.1\" data-link=\"76.1874\">Messages to Young People, 365, 366</span>.</span></a></sup>",
