    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "As they learn thus to study the lessons in all created things and in all life&apos;s experiences, show that the same laws which govern the things of nature and the events of life are to control us, that they are given for our good, and that only in obedience to them can we find true happiness and success.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">12<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ed 102.1\" data-link=\"29.485\">Education, 102, 103</span>.</span></a></sup>",
